@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Услуги";
}

<!-- Page Header Start -->
<div class="container-fluid page-header py-5 mb-5 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <h1 class="display-1 text-white animated slideInDown">Услуги</h1>
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb animated slideInDown">
            <ol class="breadcrumb text-uppercase mb-0">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a class="text-white" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Начало</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item text-primary active" aria-current="page">Услуги</li>
            </ol>
        </nav>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Page Header End -->
<!-- Team Start -->
<div class="container-xxl px-0 py-5">
    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp mx-auto text-center" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
        <div class="h-100">
            <p class="text-primary text-uppercase mb-2">Услуги</p>
            <h1 class="display-6 mb-4">НАШИТЕ УСЛУГИ</h1>
            <p>Във <span class="text-primary"><b>PHOTONIC</b></span> предлагаме разнообразие от фотографски услуги, създадени да уловят и съхранят най-ценните ви моменти.</p>
            <hr class="w-50 mx-auto mb-5 mb-xl-9 border-dark-subtle">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-0">
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/wedding.jpg" alt="wedding">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Wedding"><h4>Сватбен портрет</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 300 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Нашият фокус е върху сватбения портрет – красиви и емоционални снимки на младоженците и техните близки.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Wedding" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Wedding" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse flex-lg-row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/prom.jpg" alt="prom">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Prom"><h4>Абитуриентски бал</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 300 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Абитуриентската вечер е един от най-вълнуващите моменти в живота на всеки ученик или студент. Ще създадем красиви и стилни снимки, които ще Ви напомнят за него.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Prom" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Prom" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-lg-row-reverse">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/baptism.jpg" alt="baptism">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Baptism"><h4>Свето кръщене</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 300 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Ще уловим красивите и емоционални моменти от церемонията по Светото кръщение, както и радостта и любовта, които споделяте със семейството и приятелите си.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Baptism" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Baptism" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-lg-row-reverse">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/product.jpg" alt="product">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Product"><h4>Продукт</h4></a>
                            <h4></h4>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 50 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Вашите продукти заслужават да бъдат представени пред клиентите така, че да говорят сами за себе си. Нашите кадри ще покажат всички силни страни и функционалности на продуктите ви.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Product" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Product" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse flex-lg-row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/family.jpg" alt="familly">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Family"><h4>Семейна фотосесия</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 200 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Запечатайте специалните моменти със семеен портрет. Това е прекрасен начин да съхраните спомените заедно с вашите близки, създавайки уникален и вечен подарък.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Family" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Family" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse flex-lg-row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/event.jpg" alt="event">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Event"><h4>Събитие</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена по договаряне</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Ще се радваме да разкажем вашето събитие с нашите кадри.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Events" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Events" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/portrait.jpg" alt="individual">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Portrait"><h4>Индививуална фотосесия</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 100 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Ще работим с Вас, за да създадем портрети, които отразяват вашата същност и характер.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Portrait" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Portrait" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/bussinessPortrait.jpg" alt="bussiness portrait">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="BusinessPortrait"><h4>Бизнес портрет</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 200 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Подкрепете своя професионален имидж с въздействащ бизнес портрет. Това е повече от обикновена снимка — това е стратегически инструмент, който изгражда доверие, демонстрира увереност и укрепва личния Ви бранд.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Business" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Business" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse flex-lg-row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/automobile.jpg" alt="automotive">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="Automobile"><h4>Автомобил</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 100 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Интериор, екстериор, на паркинг, в движение по улиците - ще получите кадри, отразяващи характера на автомобила ви.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Automotive" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Automotive" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
            <div class="row g-0 flex-sm-row-reverse">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="team-img position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="~/resources/images/secret.jpg" alt="secret">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="h-100 p-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <a asp-controller="StaticContent" asp-action="SecretPhotoshoot"><h4>Тайна фотосесия</h4></a>
                            <span class="text-primary">Цена от 200 лв</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Искате да направите предложение за брак? Да изненадате приятел? Направете момента още по-изнендващ и специален, като го запечатате без знанието на другия. Непринудените реакции на хората са безценни и винаги изглеждат красиво на снимки.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="ReserveByType" asp-controller="PhotoShoot" asp-route-photoShootType="@Category.Automotive" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa fa-calendar-days"></i></a>
                            <a target="_blank" asp-action="Portfolio" asp-controller="Photo" asp-route-category="@Category.Automotive" class="btn btn-square btn-outline-primary rounded-circle me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-images"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</div>